---
// How It Works Section
// "Refine the problem. Define the solution."
// Holistic redesign: Building from user requirement down with AI-design expertise
---

<section class="how-it-works section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="big-bold-text">REFINE THE PROBLEM. DEFINE THE SOLUTION.</h2>

    <p class="intro-text">
      We build everything from user requirement down using product design thinking. Every product is different. Every business has unique patterns. We don't rush discovery—we do it right.
    </p>

    <div class="process-overview">
      <h3>The Process:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>As many proof-of-concepts as needed (typically 5-7 maximum)</li>
        <li>Each PoC validates one assumption, tests one unknown</li>
        <li>Research-driven, user-validated methodology</li>
        <li>Time-based contract ensures thoroughness</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="methodology">
      <h3>Our Methodology:</h3>
      <p class="methodology-intro">
        We build everything from user requirement down. Starting from your business foundation, we layer discovery:
      </p>

      <div class="foundation-stack" id="foundation-stack">
        <!-- Foundation Layer (Built through tests and tries) -->
        <div class="foundation-layer foundation-base">
          <span class="layer-number">01</span>
          <h5 class="layer-title">Problem Statement</h5>
          <p class="layer-description">Defining what we're really solving</p>
        </div>

        <div class="foundation-layer foundation-base">
          <span class="layer-number">02</span>
          <h5 class="layer-title">Workflow</h5>
          <p class="layer-description">How this will work in practice</p>
        </div>

        <div class="foundation-layer foundation-base data-layer">
          <span class="layer-number">03</span>
          <h5 class="layer-title">Data Foundation</h5>
          <div class="data-badges">
            <span class="badge">Management</span>
            <span class="badge">Quality</span>
            <span class="badge">Privacy</span>
            <span class="badge">Compliance</span>
            <span class="badge">Data Steward</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Middle Layer -->
        <div class="foundation-layer middle-layer">
          <span class="layer-number">04</span>
          <h5 class="layer-title">Goal & Expectation</h5>
          <p class="layer-description">What success looks like for your business</p>
        </div>

        <div class="foundation-layer middle-layer">
          <span class="layer-number">05</span>
          <h5 class="layer-title">User Requirement</h5>
          <p class="layer-description">What users actually need to succeed (starting point for building down)</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Prototyping Layer (AI-Powered) -->
        <div class="foundation-layer prototyping-layer ai-enhanced">
          <span class="layer-number">06</span>
          <h5 class="layer-title">AI-Enhanced Prototyping</h5>
          <p class="layer-description">Creating visual blueprints, service blueprints, and clickable mockup prototypes with AI-documented PRD</p>
          <div class="ai-deliverables">
            <span class="deliverable-badge">Diagrams</span>
            <span class="deliverable-badge">Service Blueprints</span>
            <span class="deliverable-badge">Clickable Mockups</span>
            <span class="deliverable-badge">AI-Documented PRD</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Top Layer -->
        <div class="foundation-layer top-layer">
          <span class="layer-number">07</span>
          <h5 class="layer-title">Operation & System → Technology & Tools</h5>
          <p class="layer-description">Real architecture designs from developers (based on client-agreed prototypes)</p>
        </div>

        <div class="foundation-layer top-layer">
          <span class="layer-number">08</span>
          <h5 class="layer-title">Control & Safety</h5>
          <p class="layer-description">Ensuring security and reliability</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Surface -->
        <div class="foundation-layer surface-layer">
          <span class="layer-number">09</span>
          <h5 class="layer-title">Product Surface</h5>
          <p class="layer-description">The final result—a product that works</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Governance Overlay (Separate, spans across) -->
      <div class="governance-overlay">
        <h4 class="governance-title">Governance | Maintenance | Improvement</h4>
        <p class="governance-description">Derived from: Data Management, Data Quality, Privacy & Compliance, Data Steward</p>
      </div>

      <p class="methodology-note">
        Each layer builds on validated insights, not assumptions. We are AI-design approach experts—using AI to create sophisticated visual blueprints and prototypes that lead to better architecture decisions.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .how-it-works {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, 
      rgba(100, 181, 246, 0.15) 0%, 
      rgba(208, 120, 85, 0.12) 100%);
    padding: var(--space-4xl) 0;
  }

  .how-it-works .big-bold-text {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .intro-text {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-text);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-4xl);
    text-align: center;
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
  }

  .process-overview {
    background: var(--color-white);
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-4xl);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent-cool);
    max-width: 800px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(19, 17, 18, 0.08);
  }

  .process-overview h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .process-overview ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .process-overview li {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--color-text);
    padding-left: var(--space-lg);
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .process-overview li::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent-warm);
    font-weight: 200;
  }

  .methodology {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: var(--space-4xl) auto 0;
  }

  .methodology h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: 200;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    text-align: center;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .methodology-intro {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
  }

  /* Foundation Stack - White Cards on Pastel Background */
  .foundation-stack {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    margin: var(--space-4xl) 0;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  /* Layer Cards - White Background */
  .foundation-layer {
    background: var(--color-white);
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent-cool);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(19, 17, 18, 0.1),
                0 2px 8px rgba(19, 17, 18, 0.06);
    position: relative;
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    animation: fadeSlideUp 0.8s ease-out forwards;
  }

  .foundation-layer:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .foundation-layer:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
  .foundation-layer:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
  .foundation-layer:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
  .foundation-layer:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.6s; }
  .foundation-layer:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 0.7s; }
  .foundation-layer:nth-child(7) { animation-delay: 0.8s; }
  .foundation-layer:nth-child(8) { animation-delay: 0.9s; }
  .foundation-layer:nth-child(9) { animation-delay: 1.0s; }

  .foundation-layer:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(19, 17, 18, 0.12),
                0 4px 16px rgba(213, 241, 86, 0.2);
    border-left-color: var(--color-accent-warm);
  }

  /* Foundation Base Layers - Slightly Emphasized */
  .foundation-base {
    border-left-color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .foundation-base:hover {
    border-left-color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  /* Middle Layers */
  .middle-layer {
    border-left-color: var(--color-accent-cool);
  }

  /* AI-Enhanced Prototyping Layer - Visually Distinct */
  .prototyping-layer.ai-enhanced {
    border-left-width: 6px;
    border-left-color: var(--color-accent-warm);
    background: linear-gradient(to right, 
      var(--color-white) 0%, 
      rgba(100, 181, 246, 0.03) 100%);
    position: relative;
  }

  .prototyping-layer.ai-enhanced::before {
    content: 'AI-Powered';
    position: absolute;
    top: var(--space-md);
    right: var(--space-md);
    background: var(--color-accent-warm);
    color: var(--color-white);
    padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-md);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 200;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .ai-deliverables {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
  }

  .deliverable-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-md);
    background: rgba(100, 181, 246, 0.1);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-accent-cool);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 200;
    color: var(--color-accent-cool);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    transition: all var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .deliverable-badge:hover {
    background: var(--color-accent-cool);
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  /* Top Layers */
  .top-layer {
    border-left-color: var(--color-accent-cool);
  }

  /* Surface Layer */
  .surface-layer {
    border-left-width: 6px;
    border-left-color: var(--color-primary);
    background: linear-gradient(to right, 
      var(--color-white) 0%, 
      rgba(26, 58, 82, 0.03) 100%);
  }

  .layer-number {
    position: absolute;
    top: var(--space-lg);
    left: var(--space-lg);
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: var(--color-accent-warm);
    color: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 200;
  }

  .layer-title {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: 200;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
    margin-left: calc(48px + var(--space-lg));
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .layer-description {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    margin-left: calc(48px + var(--space-lg));
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Data Layer Special Styling */
  .data-badges {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
    margin-left: calc(48px + var(--space-lg));
  }

  .badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-md);
    background: transparent;
    border: 2px solid var(--color-accent-cool);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 200;
    color: var(--color-accent-cool);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    transition: all var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .badge:hover {
    background: var(--color-accent-cool);
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  /* Governance Overlay */
  .governance-overlay {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    margin-top: var(--space-3xl);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-accent-cool);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(19, 17, 18, 0.1);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .governance-title {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 200;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .governance-description {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    margin: 0;
  }

  @keyframes fadeSlideUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .methodology-note {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 200;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-top: var(--space-3xl);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .layer-title {
      margin-left: 0;
      margin-top: calc(48px + var(--space-md));
    }

    .layer-description {
      margin-left: 0;
    }

    .layer-number {
      top: var(--space-md);
      left: var(--space-md);
    }

    .data-badges {
      margin-left: 0;
      justify-content: flex-start;
    }

    .ai-deliverables {
      margin-left: 0;
    }

    .prototyping-layer.ai-enhanced::before {
      position: static;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    }
  }
</style>

<script>
  // Intersection Observer for scroll-triggered animation
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    const stack = document.getElementById('foundation-stack');

    if (stack) {
      const observer = new IntersectionObserver(
        (entries) => {
          entries.forEach((entry) => {
            if (entry.isIntersecting) {
              stack.classList.add('visible');
            }
          });
        },
        { threshold: 0.1 }
      );

      observer.observe(stack);
    }
  });
</script>
